### **Advanced Networking**
```yaml
clusters:
  homelab:
    networks:
      management:
        vlan: 10
        subnet: 192.168.10.0/24
      storage:
        vlan: 20
        subnet: 192.168.20.0/24
    
    masters:
      - name: k8s-master-01
        networks:
          - interface: eth0
            network: management
            ip: 192.168.10.201
          - interface: eth1
            network: storage
            ip: 192.168.20.201
```

This hosts configuration system provides the flexibility and control needed for complex infrastructure while maintaining the simplicity and declarative nature of InfraFlux.